<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="J%20Biomed%20Inform"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Hypothesis-driven modeling of the human lung–ventilator system: A characterization tool for Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome research</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Stroh%20JN"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">JN Stroh</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">JN Stroh</span></h3>
<div class="p">
