</div>
</div>
<sup>d</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hripcsak%20G"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">George Hripcsak</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">George Hripcsak</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>e</sup>Department of Biomedical Informatics, Columbia University, New York, NY, USA</div>
